Vile Intent - Skin In The Game
Vile Intent - Skin In The Game

Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on September 19, 2013 Description from Terminal Escape:
These dudes just get meaner sounding. Cavernous powerviolence with lurching blasts, rumbling low end a level of discomfort that permeates the entire recording, but is especially evident when VILE INTENT slow down. Seven songs in as many minutes, this third cassette (the plastic shell version of the EP by the same name) came my way ages ago, and I have been remiss in not sharing it before now... SKIN IN THE GAME
